description:
100% Italian Extra Virgin Olive Oil from Italy's market leading brand, Monini. Family owned and run since 1920.

Classico 100% Italian Extra Virgin Olive Oil - balanced in flavour and suitable for everyday use in frying, roasting and dressing salads.

Since 1920 in Spoleto, Umbria, the Monini family have been dedicated to crafting the highest performing 100% Italian Extra Virgin Olive Oil.

With a strict focus on the quality of product and consistency on flavour, the task of crafting the perfect blend is personally overseen by owner and grandson of the company founder, Mr Zefferino Monini.
name: Monini Classico Extra Virgin Olive Oil 750mL
